name: Bit Mouth 11,400
description:
artonomous portrait of Bit Mouth, a
bitGAN created from the burning of
bitGANs (0o1) and (0o14). This
portrait was painted by an AI enabled
robot with 11,400 brushstrokes. It is a
mystery why the bitGANs have
suddenly begun appearing, though it
appears that they are trying to tell us
something important.
